

New Gen V4 Board
----------------

- Connector for Glove(Horizontal)
- Option for alternate Gyro/Mag (GY-85)
- Move uC to back of board
- Reduce to 1 big/1 small button
- Label GND for Glove and LED connector
- Use WS2812 2020
- Assemble SMD by JCBPCB
- Better thought through mounting holes

